uld set `java.vendor`, preventing the IBM `canLoad(...)` branch from being reached.\n\nI did not run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01c70654245d360c016a0f412f6134819dbf710bc8ebef3c98\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1511, "output": 1112, "cacheRead": 54272, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 56895, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1779384608135, "responseId": "resp_01c70654245d360c016a0f4120c42c819d9cfbdcecd7372d27"}, "toolResults": []}
