y:\n- Passing the full classpath caused `ChildFirstClassLoader` to reload unrelated runtime dependencies child-first, including `logback` and Android/Robolectric XML classes.\n- That triggered `org.apache.harmony.xml.ExpatParser` native initialization and failed with:\n  ```text\n  UnsatisfiedLinkError: org.apache.harmony.xml.ExpatParser.staticInitialize(...)\n  ```\n- The narrowed classpath still lets the child loader load a fresh copy of Kafka’s `KerberosError`, while delegating logging/XML dependencies to the parent loader.\n\nI did not run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01c70654245d360c016a0f416464c0819dbc2c0477783329b1\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1229, "output": 732, "cacheRead": 51200, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 53161, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1779384664412, "responseId": "resp_01c70654245d360c016a0f4159102c819d993543244921ba17"}}
